438
01:22:00,690 --> 01:22:02,240
I want to go home.

439
01:22:09,490 --> 01:22:11,360
Take a breath.

440
01:22:11,500 --> 01:22:15,460
Tell me what's going on.
You can talk to me.

441
01:22:20,000 --> 01:22:21,670
It was that house.

442
01:22:24,310 --> 01:22:28,370
There was something there
