your daughter Kayako.

458
01:26:47,470 --> 01:26:51,740
I saw the journal.
I know you can get rid of evil spirits.

459
01:26:54,410 --> 01:26:56,280
She is dead.

460
01:26:57,920 --> 01:27:00,080
